                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060521-55-off288 t18060521-55-cd289"></join>, three pewter pint pots, value 1 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18060521-55-victim538" type="victimName">
                     Ishmael 
                     Birch
